      <item>
        <title>R and ggplot2 pseudo code for barcode of Firefox questions</title>
        <description>&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;(please refer to my previous post:  &lt;a href=&quot;http://rolandtanglao.com/2020/10/19/p1-hourly-infographics-from-firefox-questions/&quot;&gt;What  infographics should I make from hourly FF support questions? Barcode  with a stripe for Operating System, and a stripe for hash of the  question?&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-r highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;ggplot&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;w&quot;&gt; 

